	OpenAttestation project is to provide SDK, Software Development Kit, to add cloud providers with capability of establishing hosts integrity report by remotely retrieving and verifying integrity reports saved in Host(s)' TPM.

	The SDK is expected to be integrated, and enhanced with security features, into ISVâ€™s cloud management software, and distributed by ISV to cloud providers

	The integrated ISV software is hosted and operated by cloud service providers

	For further development, please read docucuments located in ~/doc/
